re of investable assets there are however some added benefits to clients who have  million or more of investable assets we encourage you to contact us to discuss your situation and circumstances in more detail you might also want to download our infographic that illustrates what we have found to be the best fit for our clients and for us what is different about your financial planning process the combined service offering of shwm and our affiliated accounting firm creates a powerful alliance that is designed to assist you across a broad range of tax and financial topics we work closely with you to integrate our tax expertise with your financial planning and wealth management our financial planning is completely customized to your situation while the breadth of our work is significant the depth of our analysis is also substantial can you tell me when i can retire ​retirement planning is a large part of what we can do for you we will work with you to assess your situation discuss your retirement goals and prepare a thorough analysis to determine a realistic and appropriate retirement date do you charge extra for financial planning ​financial planning services are included in our fees when the client portfolio is  million or more otherwise we simply bill for financial planning services on an hourly basis and provide an estimate for those services before beginning the process can i call and ask questions yes clients are always welcome to call us we are committed to being responsive we also offer regular meetings because we want you to understand and be comfortable with your investments and overall financial plan we are also happy to meet with you outside of our offices if necessary whats the difference between shwm a registered investment adviser and a broker firm ​unlike brokerage firms we are legally held to a fiduciary standard in other words our clients interests must always come before our own we feel that this is the only way a financial advisory relationship should be structured brokerage firms must only ensure that their investments are ”suitable” widely considered a lower standard  we have virtually eliminated the sale of products so that we remain objective and avoid as many potential conflicts as possible  do you talk to me before making investment decisions when you engage shwm you grant us the discretion to make investment decisions and trades on your behalf as part of that process we will communicate to you in a timely manner the thought process behind the trading decisions we have made where is my money custodied your investment assets are typically held at charles schwab the largest custodian in the country for independent registered investment advisors our clients enjoy the peace of mind that comes from schwabs cuttingedge account security technology and administrative services for example schwabs security guarantee means that  of any loss in a schwab account due to unauthorized activity is covered if you have additional questions need clarification on any of the faqs provided above or would like to schedule some time to meet with us please call anyone on our team at  or email us related articles brad swinsburg and cecil staton at marcys mulligan marcys mulliganread more summary q complacency in investing rarely ends well  as strong as the last  months have been it is important not to extrapolate and assume that such a trend will continue  in the cartoon below that is clearly the “plan” read more smith  howard wealth management skip to main content menu call map resources contact client access after hours events search form search you are herehomeservices for institutions services for institutions our team consists of specialists in the fields of investment management financial planning tax and portfolio administration clients enjoy our open accessibility and the fact that they always have an owner of the firm involved in their financial decisions  we hold ourselves to a high standard of commitment to our clients 