oyees    in either case shwm can be a valuable partner in this process unlike many firms we do not sell or endorse proprietary products instead we serve as consultants to our business clients helping them find the right retirement plan solution that solution might be a profit sharing plan a plan with a k feature a traditional defined benefit plan or a new cash balance plan regardless our relationships with top retirement plan service providers allow us to present you with realistic options that match your needs with the services of the provider our advisors stay with you every step of the way helping you understand and address your role as fiduciary meeting with plan trustees to establish priorities helping guide development of the investment policy statement and helping the plan sponsor determine the investment lineup or investment allocation for the plan we can also assist with k conversion services searching for a new plan provider working with you and your provider on plan design changes monitoring the conversion and scheduling employee education and enrollment meetings long after your plan is in place we are still working with you to provide state of the plan review meetings quarterly performance reviews monitoring for compliance and assisting with such things as potential dol audits we commit to understanding your business needs and investment requirements but also to being available and responsive to you throughout the year you can trust shwm to be objective at all times – looking out only for your best interests related resources how business owners can defer more tax and save more for retirement it might not happen to every business owner but there are times a company is generating more profit for the owner than they can shelter in a traditional k retirement planread more imgjpg search engine marketing sem  bing ads skip to content sign upsign in   you run your business well help find your customers bing ads can help build your business and drive your succe